Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
power_integrity_place(25.10)                      power_integrity_place(25.10)

Name
       power_integrity_place  -  Calls Voltus to run irdrop analysis including
       power analysis, rail analysis, and debug IRdrop

Syntax
       power_integrity_place

       [-help]

       Calls Voltus to run irdrop  analysis  including  power  analysis,  rail
       analysis,  and  debug IRdrop. The aggressors come from the Voltus feed-
       back. Tool adds padding on the aggressors to push cell away to fix  IR-
       drop.  On  the  basis of the effort level set through this option, tool
       selects the IRdrop fixing strength flow.

       The flow involves incremental placement and refine placement.

Parameters
       -help  Outputs a brief description that includes type and  default  in-
              formation for each power_integrity_place parameter.

              For a detailed description of the command and all of its parame-
              ters, use the man command: man power_integrity_place.

